data.title: Love Wins as Veteran Nigerian Actors Joke Silva And Olu Jacobs Celebrate 35th Wedding Anniversary
data.meta_description: Veteran Nollywood actors, Joke Silva and Olu Jacobs are currently in celebration mood. The couple celebrated their 35th wedding anniversary on Monday ...
data.text:
Veteran Nollywood actors, Joke Silva and Olu Jacobs are currently in celebration mood.

The couple celebrated their 35th wedding anniversary on Monday November 16th 2020.

The gorgeous lady of style, Joke Silva took to her Instagram page to celebrate her union with her husband. She shared the lovely photo above and then wrote:

“Totally forgot. 35 years together…thank you, Lord. Here is to many more. Happy wedding anniversary Omo boy @_olujacobs.”

Happy wedding anniversary to them!

//
